K"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaruwrapN","text_ar":"حَرُورَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaraArapN","text_ar":"حَرَارَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Free persons, collectively."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hur~N","text_ar":"حُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b3-  (tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eminent, elevated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"noble persons"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the Arabs, (K, TA,) and of the foreigners. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa mino Hur~iy~api qawomihi","text_ar":"هُوَ مِنْ حُرِّيَّةِ قَوْمِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is of the noble ones of his people:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the choicest, best,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"most excellent, of his people."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Sandy, soft earth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"good, and fit to produce plants"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hur~iy~apu Albuquwli","text_ar":"حُرِّيَّةُ البُقُولِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hur~N","text_ar":"حُرٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","A","Msb","K","Mgh","MF","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}